Driving by and noticed a huge new sign "Las Vegas Buffet" so had to check it out.
Went to Check-in but surprised to find it didn't exist in Yelp!
I'm quite skeptical when it comes to Asian buffets but I was so impressed, I immediately added this business to Yelp for others to enjoy.
They've really raised the bar for a local buffet.
Awesome variety, authentic Chinese dishes, and some of the most friendly staff you can find (which surprised me since they're not really working for tips).
To top it off, it's one of the most clean and well decorated restaurants in the area.
Say what you will about this piece of information but I always know the food's going to be great when I'm the only white guy in a packed place!

